<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>한솔제약 처방전 보관 서비스</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
        }
        .main-image {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .main-content {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 4rem 3rem;
            margin-left: auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .main-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .sub-title {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .highlight-text {
            color: #0d6efd;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .feature-list {
            margin: 2rem 0;
            padding-left: 0;
        }
        .feature-list li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .feature-list li:before {
            content: "✓";
            color: #0d6efd;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .action-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .feature-icon-section {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .feature-icon-section .card {
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
        }
        @media (max-width: 991px) {
            .main-image {
                display: none;
            }
            .main-content {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <img src="/images/main.jpg" alt="메인 이미지" class="main-image">
    
    <div class="main-content">
        <h1 class="main-title">처방전 관리,<br>이제 더 쉽게 시작하세요</h1>
        <p class="sub-title">번거로운 처방전 관리 없이 편하게,</p>
        <p class="highlight-text">한솔제약 처방전 보관 서비스로 간편하게 관리하세요.</p>
        
        <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>간편한 처방전 수거 요청</li>
            <li>필요시 처방전 검색 요청</li>
            <li>요청 상태 실시간 확인</li>
            <li>알림톡을 통한 편리한 소통</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="action-card">
            <div class="d-grid gap-3">
                <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                    <a href="https://www.hansolhealthcare.co.kr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg flex-grow-1">홈페이지 바로가기</a>
                    <a href="/pharmacy/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg flex-grow-1">약국 로그인</a>
                </div>
                <a href="/pharmacy/register" class="btn btn-outline-primary">회원가입</a>
                <p class="text-center text-muted small mt-2">아직 회원이 아니신가요? 지금 바로 가입하세요!</p>
                <p class="text-center text-muted small">관리자이신가요? <a href="/admin-login" class="text-primary">관리자 로그인</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-icon-section">
            <div class="row g-3">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card text-center">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="bi bi-box-seam display-4 text-primary mb-3"></i>
                            <h6 class="card-title">간편한 처방전 수거</h6>
                            <p class="card-text small">약국에서 처방전 수거 요청 버튼만 클릭하면 담당자가 직접 방문합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card text-center">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="bi bi-shield-check display-4 text-primary mb-3"></i>
                            <h6 class="card-title">안전한 보관</h6>
                            <p class="card-text small">보안이 철저한 시설에서 처방전을 안전하게 보관합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card text-center">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="bi bi-search display-4 text-primary mb-3"></i>
                            <h6 class="card-title">빠른 처방전 검색</h6>
                            <p class="card-text small">필요한 처방전을 신속하게 찾아 이미지로 제공합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
